snippet.title: Lost and Hound - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official trailer for the investigative/mystery adventure, Lost and Hound!

Lost and Hound is an investigative adventure about searching for the things that are lost, both out in the world and within ourselves. As Biscuit, you're helping people through your ability to track down what others cannot find, using the incredibly powerful senses that dogs have.

https://twitter.com/lostandhound1
http://lostandhound1.com
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1054350/Lost_and_Hound/
